---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Whisper STT"
  description="Whisper STT's privacy policy. Learn how we protect your data — all audio processing happens locally in your browser. We never collect, store, or transmit your audio."
  canonicalUrl="/privacy-policy"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose animate-fade-in">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 10, 2026</p>

        <h2>Our Core Privacy Principle</h2>
        <p>
          Whisper STT is built on a fundamental privacy principle: <strong>your audio data never leaves your device</strong>.
          All speech recognition and translation processing happens entirely within your web browser using local AI models.
          We do not upload, store, transmit, or have access to any audio you process through our tool.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Audio files or recordings</li>
          <li>Transcription or translation results</li>
          <li>Microphone recordings</li>
          <li>Personal voice data</li>
          <li>Personally identifiable information</li>
          <li>Account information (we don't have accounts)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information We May Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect limited, non-personal information through standard web technologies:</p>

        <h3>Analytics Data</h3>
        <p>
          We may use privacy-respecting analytics to understand general site usage patterns. This may include:
          page views, approximate geographic region (country level), browser type, device type, and referring URLs.
          This data is aggregated and cannot identify individual users.
        </p>

        <h3>Advertising (Ezoic)</h3>
        <p>
          We use Ezoic as our advertising partner to display ads on our site. Ezoic may use cookies and similar
          technologies to serve personalized or non-personalized ads based on your browsing behavior.
          For more information about how Ezoic handles data, please see
          <a href="https://www.ezoic.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ezoic's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3>Model Caching</h3>
        <p>
          The Whisper AI model files are downloaded from Hugging Face's content delivery network and cached in your
          browser's local storage (Cache API / IndexedDB). These model files do not contain any personal data.
          You can clear this cache at any time through your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We may use cookies for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for basic site functionality</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> Used by Ezoic to serve and optimize ads</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics cookies:</strong> Used to understand site usage patterns</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          For more details, see our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hugging Face:</strong> Hosts the AI model files that are downloaded to your browser. See <a href="https://huggingface.co/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hugging Face Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Ezoic:</strong> Advertising platform. See <a href="https://www.ezoic.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ezoic Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          Since audio data never leaves your device, there are no servers to breach or databases to compromise.
          Your transcription data is as secure as your own device.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Whisper STT is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information
          from children.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, CCPA, and similar regulations, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access any personal data we hold about you (we hold none)</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data (nothing to delete)</li>
          <li>Opt out of personalized advertising (through your browser settings or Ezoic's controls)</li>
          <li>Clear cached model files from your browser at any time</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page
          with an updated revision date.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at
          <strong>privacy@whisperstt.com</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
